See build-config

TOOLCHAINDIR= Where your toolchains are 

TOOLCHAIN= Which toolchain in this format "arm-eabi-4.6" without quotes

CROSS_COMPILE=$TOOLCHAINDIR/$TOOLCHAIN/bin/arm-eabi-

LOCAL_BUILD_DIR= Put where your build files are usually in root of source in name of device eg, vigor toro dna

TARGET_DIR= Put where you want ZIP files to be stored here

Place the kernel directory in LOCAL_BUILD_DIR

Place rest of files in in the root of your source and run build.sh in terminal. You will find the output zip in TARGET_DIR 

This tree is complete for auto s-on detection for DNA. Must flash boot.img from AnyKernel-Boots located on internal storage to complete installation if S-On.
